name: Squidding Over It
description:
This game is a challenge for brave people. A challenge worthy of a true Squidding Master.

Do you think you have what it takes to reach the top? PROVE IT!!


In this adventure you will have to help a slippery squid to reach the stars. But be careful, because you may stumble and slip back to where you started. Prove your worth by leading this clueless squid to the top.
